    "description": "<p>Anywheel is an eco-friendly first &amp; last mile micro-mobility sharing service company. Founded in 2017 and headquartered in Singapore, the company also has a presence in Thailand.&nbsp;Anywheel has recently started powerbank sharing service in 2024.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With a career at Anywheel, it is more than just life around bicycles and powerbanks. The internet company pays great emphasis on their IoT device's (smart lock) research and development, giving employees opportunities for learning and growth in both hardware and software technologies.&nbsp;</p>",
